<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Andrew Wheeler, who now runs the EPA, is not crazy and careless like Pruitt.  He is a &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.commondreams.org/views/2018/07/06/how-dangerous-new-epa-chief-andrew-wheeler-very-heres-why&#34;&gt;careful and persistent saboteur&lt;/a&gt; for the coal business.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
