&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2018/jul/05/a-man-raped-me-another-tried-to-they-were-not-animals-they-were-men&#34;&gt;A journalist says&lt;/a&gt; that the strangers that raped her are not monsters or animals.  They are men who think they can get away with violent crime.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
