<title>Harassing black drivers</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://stallman.org/glossary.html#thug&#34;&gt;Thugs&lt;/a&gt; in the area of St Louis systematically harass black drivers by giving them lots of traffic tickets that they can&#39;t afford to pay.  They systematically allow white drivers to &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/jul/05/missouri-driving-while-black-st-louis&#34;&gt;get away with much worse&lt;/a&gt;.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
