<title>Urgent: Justice for Anthony Wall</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Everyone: &lt;a href=&#34;https://campaigns.organizefor.org/petitions/justice-for-anthony-wall&#34;&gt;Demand justice for Anthony Wall&lt;/a&gt;, who was attacked by restaurant staff and then by &lt;a href=&#34;https://stallman.org/glossary.html#thug&#34;&gt;thugs&lt;/a&gt;, apparently for being black and gay.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
