<published>2018-07-11T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-11T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Channel One&#39;s commercials</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Channel One&#39;s commercial advertisements to captive audiences in US schools are &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.commondreams.org/newswire/2018/07/05/advocates-commercial-free-schools-cheer-channel-one-signs&#34;&gt;coming to an end&lt;/a&gt;.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CJ3A6D00QWPD8QZGVVQMMD5H.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CJ3A6D00QKNPQ1NT6TEHSX1Y.html</id>
<published>2018-07-11T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-11T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Air pollution from ships</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; The engines of ships in the Mediterranean produce lots of air pollution.  This is  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jul/06/i-dont-want-ships-to-kill-me-marseille-fights-cruise-liner-pollution&#34;&gt;especially dangerous when they run their engines at a dock in a city&lt;/a&gt;, right next to where people live.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CJ3A6D00QKNPQ1NT6TEHSX1Y.html"/>
</entry>
